5.context api(single source of truth)-can have return or not(it goes to consumer and back)
func(called from lcomponet goes to hoc then returns lc)->render is called->now consumer returns to hoc(provider).
-earlier we have to pass state to lower then calling higher components.So if we need data to any lower then we have to pass too every hierarchical component till lower is reached.Ths,very hectic.
-UUse provider and consumer.Thus,provider is one and consumer is many
-using context

